formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
> All parkings are common parking. The firm is not selling parking specifically to any member.					
> We are certifying amount incurred and paid on the basis of available information provided to us and we have relied on that information. Estimated figures are provided by the promoter and we have relied on that. We have relied on information and explanation given by Promoter in relation to Estimated figures of total Cost of Construction , Estimated Sales Value , Parking Details, Type of KYC , KYC No and Mobile Number. We have not verified Agreement for Sale made if any. The Records produced before us is unaudited records and the Certificate issued is solely for the purpose of RERA requirement. Information of Block Type, Usage, Carpet Area, Area of Exclusive Balcony and Veranda, Unit Consideration, Unit wise received amount, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, allottee name, redevelopment details mentioned in Annex of Form 3 are taken as given by promoter and Promoter is responsible for the accuracy and completeness of the said information. It is not possible for us to comment or express opinion on physical progress of the project mentioned in Form 1 by Architect and cost incurred mentioned.					
> Actual RERA Bank Account number for the project Panchshil Aagam is 108001013002 but instead of this earlier wrong account number i.e. 108001015431 has been mentioned by mistake and hence this wrong account number is coming by default which I am not able to change while filing of Form-3 and hence you are requested to consider the account number 108001013002 as correct RERA Bank account number.					
> Whenever required necessary changes have been made according to information and explanation have been provided to me by the partners of the firm.
